UserOptionDefinition.Device_ExperienceSettings_FallGuys_C.Spe: Whether or not live teammates are valid spectate targets. Priority determines which spectate targets are available to a user at any point. Lower values take precedence, so players will be able to cycle between all of their priority 0 targets. If there are no priority 0 targets, they can cycle between all of their priority 1 targets, etc. This allows you to have fallbacks (e.g. if you have no alive teammates, focus on a fixed camera)
UserOptionDefinition.Device_ExperienceSettings_Lime_C.Spectat: Whether or not live teammates are valid spectate targets. Priority determines which spectate targets are available to a user at any point. Lower values take precedence, so players will be able to cycle between all of their priority 0 targets. If there are no priority 0 targets, they can cycle between all of their priority 1 targets, etc. This allows you to have fallbacks (e.g. if you have no alive teammates, focus on a fixed camera)
